release_notes:
This release contains many improvements and fixes.

**Notable updates**

- Fix an issue where the check for updates button stopped working after entering certain flows.
- Added DNS Logs to Preferences UI.
- View logs now correctly shows the contents of the zip file uploaded when you submit logs (you can manually trigger this by running warp-diag).
- Submit feedback will cache feedback and send the next time we are able to connect.
- New Bypass WARP for local network connectivity checkbox added to Preferencesâ†’Advanced allowing you to decide if WARP should allow local traffic.
- A number of High Sierra and Mojave compatibility fixes.
- DoH Subdomain is now populated by default when registering your device with Cloudflare for Teams (NOTE you can still override this value).
- Improved handling of plist when changes are made after client is running.
- 5 Device limit is now enforced when sharing your license key.

**Known issues**

- You are unable to subscribe to WARP+ via the Desktop apps. You must subscribe first on your mobile device and then copy/paste your license key into the Accounts page on desktop.
- Localization parity with mobile is coming in a future update.
- Wired networks via a USB dongle are not excluded properly.

For a complete list of known issues please visit https://developers.cloudflare.com/warpclient/known-issues-and-faq
